Usage: Mikrotik_BandwidthTest.py [options] HOST

Options:
  -h, --help            show this help message and exit
  -p PORT, --port=PORT
  -t DURATION, --time=DURATION
                        test duration in seconds
  -m MTU, --mtu=MTU
  -d DIRECTION, --direction=DIRECTION
                        test direction: receive, send, both
